<p>John and Dave end out June with this packed Premium episode. Topics include AppleCare advice and discounts, setting your own shortcut keys, advice for Mac consultants, and more! If you&rsquo;re not already subscribed, it&rsquo;s just $25 for 6 months of additional content from your two favorite geeks!</p>
